name: The Last Piece
description:
Yes! I am a DEMON but I have a tale to tell!
Love showed me heavens and threw me in hell!

Love is Beautiful, it creates, it dosen't destroy.
Humans destroy.
I want to give a message through this piece that self destruction is not the solution. The pain that loves gives us should be channelized for self construction instead. 
I have been there and understand the agony, hence the advice.
Healing and light to all.
Much love <3
